<script setup lang="ts">
import { computed, ref } from 'vue'
import { capacitanceCode } from '@/calculators/capacitance'
const value=ref(''); const factor=ref(1e-12); const units=[{label:'pF',factor:1e-12},{label:'nF',factor:1e-9},{label:'μF',factor:1e-6},{label:'mF',factor:1e-3},{label:'F',factor:1}]
const farads=computed(()=>Number(value.value)*factor.value); const valid=computed(()=>Number.isFinite(farads.value)&&farads.value>0)
function format(unitFactor:number):string{return valid.value?Number((farads.value/unitFactor).toPrecision(12)).toLocaleString('zh-CN',{maximumFractionDigits:12}):'—'}
</script>
<template><section class="converter-layout"><div class="panel"><div class="panel-toolbar"><div><h2>电容换算器</h2><p>输入任意一种单位，实时换算全部常用电容单位</p></div><span class="circuit-type">1 μF = 1000 nF = 1,000,000 pF</span></div><label class="converter-source"><span>输入电容值</span><div class="value-with-unit"><input v-model="value" type="number" min="0" step="any"><select v-model.number="factor"><option v-for="unit in units" :key="unit.label" :value="unit.factor">{{ unit.label }}</option></select></div></label><div class="conversion-results"><div v-for="unit in units" :key="unit.label"><span>{{ unit.label }}</span><strong>{{ format(unit.factor) }}</strong></div></div><div class="capacitor-code"><span>常用三位电容代码</span><strong>{{ valid?capacitanceCode(farads):'—' }}</strong><p>代码以 pF 为基准，前两位为有效数字，第三位为追加零的个数。例如 104 = 100 nF。</p></div></div><aside class="panel conversion-guide"><h2>快速参照</h2><dl><div><dt>1 F</dt><dd>1000 mF</dd></div><div><dt>1 mF</dt><dd>1000 μF</dd></div><div><dt>1 μF</dt><dd>1000 nF</dd></div><div><dt>1 nF</dt><dd>1000 pF</dd></div></dl><p>μF 也常写作 uF；电容本体上的 102、103、104 等标记通常采用三位 pF 代码。</p></aside></section></template>
